raft.jpct.bones
Class Skeleton

java.lang.Object
  raft.jpct.bones.Skeleton
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Iterable<Joint>
public class Skeleton
extends Object
implements Serializable, Iterable<Joint>

A collection of Joint's which constitute a hierarchy. A Skeleton can be shared among SkeletonPoses.

This class is originally adapted from Ardor3D.
